-KGraph.\n  We built SED-KGraph in a crowd-sourced project with 170 contributors from\nboth academia and industry. The experiment results indicate that our solutions\noutperform baselines that neglect the semantic relationships among topics by at\nleast 25% and 23% in terms of ASR and MAP metrics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 19:54:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 13:28:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
