nce of MRI turbulence. Finally, we find that\n$\\alpha$-$\\text{Pm}$ scaling is sensitive to the box vertical-to-radial aspect\nratio, as well as to the background shear.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2022 13:50:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2022 09:39:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
